<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to MultiMart</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555555;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to MultiMart</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>MultiMart</strong> — we’re excited to have you on
          board!
        </p>
        <p>
          To complete your registration, please use the activation code below:
        </p>
        <h2><%= otp %></h2>
        <p>
          Enter this code on the activation page within the next
          <strong>5 minutes</strong> to activate your account.
        </p>
        <p>
          Didn’t sign up for a MultiMart account? No worries — just ignore this
          email.
        </p>
        <p>
          Need help? Reach out to us anytime at
          <a href="mailto:support@multimart.com">support@multimart.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you,<br />The MultiMart Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        &copy; 2025 MultiMart. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
